{"tid":2416341,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"牛三其實係比散戶追趕大戶回報率既捷徑黎","createTime":"2021-02-21T03:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T03:33:58.000Z","uid":81236,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"87c7dac7ef8a5229c7b3b149199964f1c9533991","tid":2416341,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:17:05.000Z","msg":"落得場就唔好怯<br />\n只係驚牛三之後既股災<br />\n怯就輸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n牛三前得好少散戶長期跑得贏大戶<br />\n有既多數都係專業人士<br />\n人地平均回報率成10%<br />\n<br />\n但牛三就唔同<br />\n散戶只要中一隻都分分鐘100% 以上<br />\n<br />\n一次過追返過去十幾年跑輸既回報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大戶做唔到因為佢地唔可以想只專注某幾隻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n牛三只後好多方法大戶可以做對沖<br />\n但多數散戶就只係得個坐字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以要贏就係牛三賺到盡<br />\n然後係你覺得股災來臨前或者第一刻斬手指<br />\n<br />\n等到股災後再入返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n長期拉返匀先可以跑贏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你話係唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693dfc88aaf2c55def4d50ad73a50ee1532e1ce6","tid":2416341,"uid":81236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:18:29.000Z","msg":"見咁多巴老都變廢老<br />\n<br />\n就知一年大家回報率已經跑贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80378ba432de8a0c2db4c57eaa40e8c1b95b1983","tid":2416341,"uid":126329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:19:25.000Z","msg":"你都幾幽默 你個本升1000% 都唔會夠大戶升10%多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb70e96bea98fdab6794719aba24bb0dc1aee81","tid":2416341,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80378ba432de8a0c2db4c57eaa40e8c1b95b1983","tid":2416341,"uid":126329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:19:25.000Z","msg":"你都幾幽默 你個本升1000% 都唔會夠大戶升10%多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:20:21.000Z","msg":"你中六合彩都唔會變李嘉誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4244e77acb9b81a777962ea2ffc8080bbbb89d","tid":2416341,"uid":92007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:21:14.000Z","msg":"問題係無人分到係股災定係中小型correction嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講就易"},{"pid":"b0b1b0af7d2a0d3cc0da355a999799e8ca6fcba4","tid":2416341,"uid":206552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:21:16.000Z","msg":"你個本越大, 你個回報率就越難高"},{"pid":"9967c33c20b7c37e768f622b4819b71b4fb2a237","tid":2416341,"uid":193227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:23:26.000Z","msg":"以為講緊牛腩3號<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e120e44cbef1098cdbb0da2f613360a92e1fcfe","tid":2416341,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9967c33c20b7c37e768f622b4819b71b4fb2a237","tid":2416341,"uid":193227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:23:26.000Z","msg":"以為講緊牛腩3號<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:33:58.000Z","msg":"佢已經失左蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}